# 🛠 User Manual - Ghost Proxy Scraper & Checker  

## 🔹 Introduction  
This tool is a Python-based Proxy Scraper & Checker developed by **GHOST x KAMAL** from **Bangladesh Cyber Troops**.  
It can scrape fresh proxies (HTTP, HTTPS, SOCKS4, SOCKS5) from free online sources, test them in real-time, and save working proxies for penetration testing, secure browsing, or bug bounty projects.  

---

## 🔹 Requirements  
- Python 3.8+  
- pip (Python package manager)  
- Linux / Windows / macOS / Termux supported  

### Install dependencies  
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt


🔹 python3 proxytool.py

🔹 Features

🔥 Multi-threaded Proxy Scraper (fast)

🌐 Supports HTTP, HTTPS, SOCKS4, SOCKS5

⚡ Real-time Proxy Checking

📁 Saves working proxies in working_proxies.txt

🔒 Authentication system (only authorized users can run)

💻 Cross-platform (Linux, Windows, macOS, Termux)



🔹 Example Output
[*] Scraping fresh proxies...
[*] Total proxies found: 450
[*] Checking proxies (multi-threaded)...
[+] Working proxies saved: working_proxies.txt




🔹 Notes

This tool is for educational & ethical use only.

Do not use it for illegal purposes.

